{"name": "Lionized", "pages": [{"name": "Lionized", "type": "text", "title": {"show": false, "level": 1}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>&#x1F981; Lionized &#x1F981;</p><ul><li>Whenever you cause a creature to become lionized, choose one of its six attributes to accentuate. Once per turn the lionized creature can add a bonus 1d4 to the result of an attack roll or check that uses the chosen attribute.&nbsp;</li><li>While a lionized creature is performing a desperate action, it can choose to take advantage on one roll at the cost of the lionized effect ending at the end of the desperate action.</li><li>The die increases in size at the second growth level, becoming a d6 at 11th level.</li></ul><p>Lionized does not stack. If a creature gains the lionized effect while already lionized, the effect with the longer duration remains. When this happens, it can also change which attribute is affected.</p>", "markdown": ""}, "_id": "KYOEYE0M3E9XAQ1G", "image": {}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "system": {}, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": -1}, "flags": {}}], "ownership": {"default": 0}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "_id": "ZOBZ8V2YME5YOYZR", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
{"name": "Villainized", "pages": [{"name": "Villainized", "type": "text", "title": {"show": false, "level": 1}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>&#x1F9FF; Villainized &#x1F9FF;</p><ul><li>Whenever a villainized creature takes damage, you can cause it to suffer 1d4 psychic damage.&nbsp;</li><li>Each time you activate this bonus damage, you can&rsquo;t trigger it again until the villainized creature has made an attack or targeted an unwilling creature with a spell or ability since the last time it took the damage.</li><li>The die increases in size at each growth level, becoming a d6 at 5th level, d8 at 11th level, and d10 at 17th level.</li></ul><p>Villainized does not stack. If a creature gains the villainized effect while already villainized, only the effect with the longer remaining duration remains.</p>", "markdown": ""}, "_id": "ADTSW8R6K1YAMW44", "image": {}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "system": {}, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": -1}, "flags": {}}], "ownership": {"default": 0}, "folder": null, "sort": 0, "_id": "WHN3T2G6R8HUKOQX", "_stats": {"systemId": "undertaking", "systemVersion": "1.0.0", "coreVersion": "11.304"}}
